      <title>开发商华南城债务减免后面临更多考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/developer-china-south-city-avoids-dollar-bond-default-scmp-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[深圳市部分持股的华南城控股有限公司在债权人同意延长美元债券期限并降低票面利率后获得了缓刑，避免了违约，因为该公司很快将面临更多的付款测试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/developer-china-south-city-avoids-dollar-bond-default-scmp-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 03:31:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丰田在其附属公司陷入安全丑闻后发誓进行改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/daihatsu-halts-all-shipments-on-safety-test-scandal-asahi-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在子公司大发汽车公司被迫暂停所有发货后，丰田汽车公司承诺进行“根本性改革”——现在面临着政府对其办公室的突袭——调查发现，该公司的大部分车辆都没有经过适当的碰撞安全测试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/daihatsu-halts-all-shipments-on-safety-test-scandal-asahi-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 02:46:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲债券和股票因降息押注而上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三欧洲股市上涨，欧元区债券收益率下跌，因经济数据恶化和通胀放缓凸显了明年降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 22:31:04 GMT</pubDate>
